Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Administrator

    public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A Student interacts with the Jukebox and requests Songs to be played. They are only allowed 1500 minutes of song time.
    Author:
    Michelle Monteith and Jamie David
    See Also:
